---
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Image/Card -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-orange-500/20 dark:bg-orange-500/10 rounded-2xl blur-xl"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <img
              src="/images/goodness-ojonuba-portrait.webp"
              alt="Goodness Ojonuba"
              width="64"
              height="64"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="h-16 w-16 rounded-xl object-cover object-top ring-2 ring-orange-500/30"
            />
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Goodness Ojonuba</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Cloud & DevOps Engineer</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
              <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Nigeria</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Open to Remote Collaborations</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">AWS Solutions Architect Associate</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">39</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Repositories</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">2</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Certifications</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">12</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Articles</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right: Content -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
          About <span class="text-orange-500">Me</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          I'm a Cloud and DevOps Engineer with a passion for building reliable, scalable infrastructure. 
          My background in IT Support gives me a unique perspective on reliability and user-centric systems 
          — skills I now apply to cloud engineering and DevOps practices.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          I specialize in Infrastructure as Code using Terraform and Ansible, CI/CD pipeline automation, 
          container orchestration with Kubernetes, and cloud-native architecture on AWS. I believe in 
          treating infrastructure as software — versioned, tested, and deployed with the same rigor as 
          application code.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Currently, I'm exploring agentic DevOps workflows using AI tools like Claude Code to automate 
          infrastructure auditing, security scanning, and deployment validation. I'm always looking for 
          opportunities to collaborate on challenging cloud and DevOps projects.
        </p>
        
        <div class="pt-4">
          <a 
            href="/about" 
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-600 font-semibold transition-colors"
          >
            Read Full Story
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
